{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTag","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Appearances","anchor":"Appearances"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"emphasized"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"primary or high-priority information.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"muted"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Status","anchor":"Status"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Neutral"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"status needs to be communicated."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Accent","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Positive","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"completed actions or approved items.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Warning","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requiring user awareness or intervention.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Negative"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"problems or failed actions."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Info","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or contextual information."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Disabled","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"allowed when loader is activated."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Shape","anchor":"Shape"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two shapes:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Rounded","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Square"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Size","anchor":"Size"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags can have two sizes:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Default","type":"text"}]},{"text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Small","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when grouping elements visually."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Layout","anchor":"Layout"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are four available layouts for tags:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"-","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text only","type":"text"}]},{"text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"elements.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Bullet"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"next to the label."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Icon","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as status, type, or action."}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Loader","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/7565ce-tag"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Orange"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange Business Tools","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_OrangeBusinessTools"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Sosh"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Wireframe"}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"name":"Version","style":"note"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.18.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Since","style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSTag","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSTag","symbolKind":"struct","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents7OUDSTagV"},"abstract":[{"text":"A tag is a small element that shows short information like a label, keyword, or category.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It helps users quickly find, group, or understand content.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstag"]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Structures","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Status"],"anchor":"Structures"},{"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(label:status:appearance:shape:size:hasLoader:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(loadingLabel:shape:size:)"],"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Enumerations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/docu